<p>
<note n="0781008" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0781008">復＝若【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note>
<note n="0781009" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0781009">坐＋（坐）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note>
